### Requires the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client).
### With backend running (F5 in VS Code, or `uvicorn app.main:app --reload`),
### click "Send Request" above any block below.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### 2. Seed demo HCPs (run once)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/dev/seed

### 3. List HCPs -- copy an "id" from the response for the requests below
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hcps

### 4. Create an interaction via the structured-form path
# Replace hcp_id with a real id from step 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/interactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hcp_id": "REPLACE_WITH_HCP_ID",
  "channel": "form",
  "interaction_type": "in_person_visit",
  "raw_notes": "Discussed CardioFlow 10mg for elderly hypertensive patients. Dr. was receptive but wants efficacy data for over-65s before prescribing. Left 15 samples.",
  "products_discussed": ["CardioFlow 10mg"]
}

### 5. List interactions for that HCP
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/interactions?hcp_id=REPLACE_WITH_HCP_ID

### 6. Edit an interaction -- replace interaction_id from step 4/5's response
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/interactions/REPLACE_WITH_INTERACTION_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products_discussed": ["CardioFlow 20mg"],
  "edited_by": "field_rep_demo",
  "reason": "Corrected dosage"
}

### 7. Chat with the agent (non-streaming) -- watch it call log_interaction itself
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "demo-session-1",
  "hcp_id": "REPLACE_WITH_HCP_ID",
  "message": "Just met Dr. Kapoor, discussed GlucoBalance, he seemed neutral and asked about pricing. Follow up in 3 weeks."
}
